data.description: Experience the pinnacle of convenience in this meticulously maintained 2-bed, 2-bath Quad Townhome. Centrally located near shopping centers and major highways with a LOW HOA, it offers affordability and accessibility. Each Bedroom features a private balcony with an interlocked bathroom in between that features dual sinks. Well-kept appliances, including two fridges, streamline daily life. Recent upgrades include a new water heater, and the property was renovated recently. With a convenient downstairs laundry room, this home effortlessly blends style and functionality. Do Not miss the opportunity to make this your own humble abode!
